    </div>
  </header>
  <main class="px-52 mx-auto min-w-0 max-w-screen-xl">
    <section class="mb-56 mt-56">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mx-auto mb-8">
        Instalar y Personalizar Git
      </h2>
      <ul class="pl-5">
        <li class="mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div
              class="bg-black rounded-full h-5 w-5 flex justify-center items-center mr-3"
            >
              <p class="font-bold text-white">1</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
              Instalar <b>Git</b>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col pl-8 mt-4">
            <a
              class="decoration-blue-700 underline decoration-solid text-blue-500 text-sm"
              href="https://git-scm.com/download/win"
              target="_blank">Descargar para windows</a
            >
            <a
              class="decoration-blue-700 underline decoration-solid text-blue-500 text-sm"
              href="https://git-scm.com/download/mac"
              target="_blank">Descargar para mac</a
            >
            <a
              class="decoration-blue-700 underline decoration-solid text-blue-500 text-sm"
              href="https://git-scm.com/download/linux"
              target="_blank">Descargar para linux</a
            >
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            2 - Abrir la consola <b>Git Bash</b>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-6">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            3 - Personalizar <b>Git</b>
          </p>
          <pre><code class="git">git config --global user.name
git config --global user.email correo</code></pre>
        </li>
      </ul>
